# **How to run this program**

# program 1

## this program take as input config file 
##inside file have a ear mouth size and port number
## current system size=1 
## if want to run as tow system want to change port as file in urecv.c and usend.c file


**baby0:**

#modify brain program only:

# first compile all:
'''bash
gcc urecv.c -o urecv
gcc baby0.c -o baby0
gcc usend.c -o usend
'''

# then run:
'''bash

./urecv
./baby0 config.txt
./usend

'''

# inside  of config file"
'''bash
EAR_PORT=6000
MOUTH_PORT=5000
REMOTE_IP=127.0.0.1
SELF_SIZE=1
BUFLEN=1022
'''

#change as per ear and mouth port 




#program 2:

**baby1.c

## this program send massage as chunk as 1024 as limit one time


#compile first:
'''bash
gcc baby1.c -o baby1
'''
#run on 1st terminal:
'''bash
./baby [send_port] [recv_port]
'''

#run 2nd terminal:
'''bash
./baby1 [recv_port] [send_port]
'''
#**USE  SAME PORT NUMBER FOR [recv_port]&[send_port]**



#program 3rd:

##this progarm can run in multiple terminal they show in first terminal other system are online


#baby2.c

#compile first:
'''bash
gcc baby2.c -o baby2
'''

#run this file more then 1  terminal
'''bash
./baby2
'''


## Brain program

#compile
'''bash
gcc urecv.c -o urecv
gcc usend.c -o usend
gcc brain.c -o brain
'''
#run one by one
'''bash
./urecv
./brain
./usend
'''



